{"tid":667744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【石棺藏屍案】主審法官突因健康理由不能審　案件須解散陪審團","createTime":"2018-05-17T04:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T04:44:29.000Z","uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e729495625c3c2e2824a9ccd76c5f211f4b4bf","tid":667744,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"【石棺藏屍案】主審法官突因健康理由不能審　案件須解散陪審團<br />\n荃灣Dan6工廈石屎藏屍案，原已進入辯方案情，今（17日）卻出現突發情況，今天開庭時出現法庭的並非主審法官李瀚良，而是審理梁天琦暴動案的法官彭寶琴，彭官先向律師交待，指李官因為健康理由，須接受即時治療，未能在短期內回歸工作，之後她待陪審團到達時，再下令解散陪審團，並把案件押後及須覓日期重審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/189332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F189332&d=28MNBqwg5GCie43WYRViMp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c67b239b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/189332</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e26cb6e9c4fdf0f7da14befe81f62404e48fe9","tid":667744,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"懷疑法官收咗兩億走佬"}]}